entries.arrived_at_loc: pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < pcontrast1 Enemy ships dropping out of hyperspace.  Stay at this location at all costs pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 Enemy ships detected on attack vector. pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_stopped: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 Scanning... No enemies detected in system. Scanning ... pcontrast3 >
entries.first_attack: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 Hyperspace surge detected. pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc: pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < pcontrast1 Excellent, the counter attack has been scrambled.  Go to this position, it will cause the attack craft to make multiple jumps and stagger the assault. pcontrast3 >
entries.mission_complete: pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < pcontrast1 That appears to be the last of them. pcontrast3 >

entries.outofrange_failed: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 The Black Sun have detected our movements and are breaking the ambush, our mission has failed. pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_defendpoint_d: You must survive the onslaught over a period of several minutes
entries.quest_location_d: An area of near disorder near the planet of Dathomir
entries.quest_reachpoint_d: Travel to this point for the confrontation, it will keep the whole attacking fleet from assaulting at once
entries.split_quest_alert: pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < pcontrast1 We're very impressed! Good work, pilot. Now that we have the weapons, we need get them to the proper facilities. We have a Lancer on its way out to meet you. pcontrast3 >
entries.title: Dathomir System: Survive the Black Sun Assault
entries.title_d: Survive against the Black Sun assault
entries.transmission_received: pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < pcontrast1 We are detecting no more hyperspace surges. pcontrast3 >
entries.transmission_start: pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < pcontrast1 The assault waves are on your position now! pcontrast3 >
